In BBj 12.00 and higher, this method returns the name and version of 
 the protocol the request uses in the form protocol/majorVersion.minorVersion, 
 for example, HTTP/1.1.[Docs](https://documentation.basis.cloud/BASISHelp/WebHelp/bbjobjects/Servlet/bbjhttprequest/BBjHttpRequest_getProtocol.htm)

In BBj 12.00 and higher, this method returns the name of the scheme used 
 to make this request in the <a href="bbjhttprequest.htm">BBjHttpRequest</a>, 
 for example, HTTP, HTTPS, or FTP.[Docs](https://documentation.basis.cloud/BASISHelp/WebHelp/bbjobjects/Servlet/bbjhttprequest/BBjHttpRequest_getScheme.htm)
